OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny morning showers clearing to
OL,6,Fleave a mainly dry and bright day,
OL,7,Fwith some sunny spells. Perhaps some
OL,8,Fmore prolonged spells of sunshine
OL,9,Fdeveloping by late afternoon. Feeling
OL,10,Fwarmer than Tuesday.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA fine and bright evening,
OL,13,Fbut then turning cloudy with outbreaks
OL,14,Fof rain developing towards midnight.
OL,15,FRain continuing overnight and turning
OL,16,Frather breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
